{"tid":1667664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[1022再黨鐵靜坐] 補番今日靜坐唔到天日再黨鐵靜坐?","createTime":"2019-10-21T14:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:34:18.000Z","uid":229436,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd42e115bd8cbc874b9edb4d7cb95b31cb1ae76","tid":1667664,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">補番今日靜坐唔到天日再黨鐵靜坐<br />\n補番今日靜坐唔到天日再黨鐵靜坐<br />\n補番今日靜坐唔到天日再黨鐵靜坐<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽住啦我地有可能再靜坐架 可能架 但都可能唔靜坐架 到天日咪知大家會唔會靜坐囉</span><br />\n或者天日唔坐咪後日囉 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7:30 黨鐵靜坐 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n天日靜坐唔到就1023 1024 1025 1026 1027 1028 1029 1030<br />\n<br />\n我睇你政府封路封得幾耐 我地依家就日日都會吹雞靜坐 你咪日日封路囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3368ec2b02212caaae8855ae2d4eb3ddf6d1e4dd","tid":1667664,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2c8cc4e97b781e5e4673d2b6df9c8a32a30c8","tid":1667664,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3c1dfbe7bc777ac675f2ad39182546c264cf2e7","tid":1667664,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"打字都有鄉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49977619ba4699c78e5487a4a2292474e385400e","tid":1667664,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba72605dffee35975c35539aab008ab55286e3e","tid":1667664,"uid":120972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"天你老母閪日"},{"pid":"faa04563b3429d6a3d2daa043e9007a4d2750c07","tid":1667664,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:57:36.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"f5baafe736c0ed524eb9165186b9ed9a3d0c7b79","tid":1667664,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af126a65103d241c4895956f3fd3413c52864ef8","tid":1667664,"uid":266154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"1022 730元朗站見"}]}